content.description: Sealed by Luminaire in ancient times to contain the darkness within, these underground ruins are now accessible, but so is the outside world to the evil from the depths.

fields.name: Available Items
fields.value: Shadow Servant, Academy Badge, Armor, Torrona's Box, Empty Tome, Attractorb, Crown, Skull O Maniac, Stone Mask, Prismatic Missile

fields.name: Unlock
fields.value: Break the Seal of the Lake (In Lake Foscari) with Keitha

fields.name: Seals
fields.value:
Seal of Abyss (Bottom Left) break with Maruto to unlock **Luminaire (Character)**
Seal of the banished (Up from seal of abyss) break with Eleanor to spawn a boss and unlock **Genevieve**
